SECURITY DISCLAIMER:

This software is provided as a proof-of-concept and educational implementation
of end-to-end encrypted chat. While it implements modern cryptographic 
primitives (ChaCha20-Poly1305, HKDF-SHA256, TLS 1.3), it has NOT been 
professionally audited for security vulnerabilities.

DO NOT USE IN PRODUCTION without:
1. Professional security audit
2. Proper key management infrastructure
3. Valid TLS certificates from trusted CAs
4. Comprehensive threat modeling
5. Regular security updates

The authors assume NO LIABILITY for any security breaches, data loss, or
damages resulting from the use of this software.

USE AT YOUR OWN RISK.
